item.title: Spawn point
item.dc:creator: @William.D William.D
item.description:
@William.D wrote:

I changed the spawn point in player.java but i doenst change :S

Here a piece of my player.java ; 

	// initial x and y coordinates of the player
		heightLevel = 0;
		// the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet
		teleportToX = 3210;//3072;
		teleportToY = 3424;//3312;

		// client initially doesn't know those values yet
		absX = absY = -1;
		mapRegionX = mapRegionY = -1;
		currentX = currentY = 0;
		resetWalkingQueue();
	}
